commit.message:
HTML typos and avoid standards.h breakage

From-SVN: r40327

@@ -1,3 +1,15 @@

+

+	entities.

+	* fixinc/fixincl.x: Regenerate.
+

 	* configure.in (HAVE_AS_LEB128): New assembler check.
